00:22:14,716 --> 00:22:18,435
I have no master.
So I have betrayed no one.

260
00:22:19,894 --> 00:22:25,532
So, tell me...
My horses, they arrive tonight?

261
00:22:28,604 --> 00:22:30,698
It's been thirty years.

262
00:22:31,447 --> 00:22:35,391
