has lived in shame and dishonor.

263
00:22:35,511 --> 00:22:38,455
All because of Shiro's treachery.

264
00:22:38,575 --> 00:22:41,740
Tonight, I will take back
what was stolen from my family...

265
00:22:41,836 --> 00:22:44,153
and everything
will change from here on.

266
00:22:44,273 --> 00:22:48,069
Shiro's men will protect his
treasure with their lives.

267
00:22:49,975 --> 00:22:53,416
Are you certain you can deliver them?

268
00:22:53,536 --> 00:22:56,029
I said I would.

269
00:22:56,319 --> 00:22:58,427
These two are the Ti brothers.

270
00:22:58,619 --> 00:23:00,633
They will give you everything you need.

271
00:23:03,246 --> 00:23:04,756
I'll be in touch.

272
00:23:14,634 --> 00:23:16,073
Watch him closely.

273
00:23:17,991 --> 00:23:20,197
SHIRO'S ESTATE
YAKUZA COMPOUND

274
00:23:20,293 --> 00:23:22,402
TO-DAI, JAPAN

275
00:23:49,492 --> 00:23:51,182
[In Japanese] I beg your forgiveness.

276
00:23:56,256 --> 00:23:58,917
The fault is not yours, but mine.

277
00:23:59,037 --> 00:24:00,859
I left myself unguarded.

278
00:24:16,072 --> 00:24:18,218
I trust you have
news from San Francisco...

279
00:24:18,338 --> 00:24:21,670
Yes, everything is
proceeding as requested.

280
00:24:21,862 --> 00:24:22,725
...and the Horses?

281
00:24:22,821 --> 00:24:24,164
We've shipped them out.

282
00:24:24,284 --> 00:24:27,233
They will arrive
in San Francisco tonight.

283
00:24:27,532 --> 00:24:30,589
You must return to San Francisco
in advance of my arrival.

284
00:24:30,709 --> 00:24:32,699
But, Father...

285
00:24:32,819 --> 00:24:36,799
I don't trust our people there.

286
00:24:37,054 --> 00:24:39,988
They have become
too lazy to be useful.

287
00:24:40,319 --> 00:24:45,454
I was hoping to stay here
and further my role in the clan.

288
00:24:45,845 --> 00:24:50,345
Nothing in the history of our clan
has ever been more important.

289
00:24:50,692 --> 00:24:52,743
I will not fail you.

290
00:24:52,956 --> 00:24:56,003
Go now.
Oversee the sale of the Horses.

291
00:25:04,922 --> 00:25:07,416
CHINA TOWN
SAN FRANCISCO

292
00:25:26,117 --> 00:25:28,035
Hey, what's up, dude?

293
00:25:28,227 --> 00:25:29,953
I need to see Benny.

294
00:25:30,049 --> 00:25:31,487
No Bennys here.

295
00:25:41,461 --> 00:25:42,420
Again!

296
00:25:44,338 --> 00:25:45,489
What are you doing?

297
00:25:46,065 --> 00:25:47,503
No!

298
00:25:47,599 --> 00:25:48,270
Yeah!

299
00:25:48,558 --> 00:25:49,901
Again!

300
00:25:50,380 --> 00:25:52,778
Come one. Oww! Ooh!

301
00:25:52,874 --> 00:25:53,929
Hey, babe.

302
00:25:58,053 --> 00:25:59,491
We need to talk.

303
00:25:59,611 --> 00:26:02,080
Cabron, I don't talk to the Feds.

304
00:26:02,176 --> 00:26:03,327
Go!

305
00:26:04,478 --> 00:26:06,108
Somewhere private.

306
00:26:06,971 --> 00:26:07,739
Now.

307
00:26:09,465 --> 00:26:10,808
Okay.

308
00:26:13,493 --> 00:26:15,986
My guy's losing anyway, so...

309
00:26:22,987 --> 00:26:25,001
I'm paying for this shit. Come on!

310
00:26:37,600 --> 00:26:39,014
Business is good, I see.

311
00:26:39,134 --> 00:26:41,762
Yeah. So much
