01:10:42,978 --> 01:10:44,992
Mommy loves you, okay. Just...

790
01:10:50,488 --> 01:10:51,322
No!

791
01:11:04,752 --> 01:11:06,738
Chang is dead.

792
01:11:06,858 --> 01:11:09,064
And the woman and child?

793
01:11:09,256 --> 01:11:11,270
Take me to the bodies
so I can take their heads.

794
01:11:12,743 --> 01:11:16,736
No. I killed them.
I should have that honor.

795
01:11:25,272 --> 01:11:26,518
Come on! Kill him!

796
01:11:57,399 --> 01:12:02,386
Are you okay? Where is my husband?

797
01:12:37,199 --> 01:12:38,541
Where's Clark?

798
01:12:38,637 --> 01:12:39,668
He's on his way back.

799
01:12:39,788 --> 01:12:40,843
He send the photos?

800
01:12:40,939 --> 01:12:42,090
Yes, sir.

801
01:12:43,270 --> 01:12:44,943
What the fuck happened up there?

802
01:12:45,063 --> 01:12:48,323
Looks like Rogue took out Chang and
turned on Shiro's assassins.

803
01:12:48,515 --> 01:12:51,464
He's using them.
Playing both sets against each other.

804
01:12:51,584 --> 01:12:52,735
Why would he do that?

805
01:12:54,444 --> 01:12:57,242
John! You're never gonna believe
who just flew in.

806
01:13:10,564 --> 01:13:14,121
Father, I'm so happy to see you.

807
01:13:14,241 --> 01:13:16,998
And I am happy to see you.

808
01:13:17,118 --> 01:13:19,675
This country looks very beautiful.

809
01:13:19,795 --> 01:13:22,273
Your English is improving.

810
01:13:22,465 --> 01:13:23,890
I have been practicing.

811
01:13:24,010 --> 01:13:26,013
This is my new home after all.

812
01:13:28,506 --> 01:13:31,012
Rogue insisted on
delivering the Horses himself.

813
01:13:31,132 --> 01:13:33,589
You've made me very proud.

814
01:13:33,685 --> 01:13:36,466
I must ask for one more thing of you.

815
01:13:36,562 --> 01:13:38,289
Anything.

816
01:13:38,384 --> 01:13:39,823
Return to Japan.

817
01:13:41,055 --> 01:13:44,906
But I want to stay with you.

818
01:13:45,098 --> 01:13:47,879
If I am to oversee our expansion here

819
01:13:47,999 --> 01:13:51,044
I need someone
who can insure our interests in Japan.

820
01:13:51,671 --> 01:13:55,314
The only person
I can trust is you, Kira.

821
01:13:55,434 --> 01:13:58,140
Shiro Yanagawa!

822
01:13:58,236 --> 01:14:01,462
FBI Special Agent John Crawford.

823
01:14:01,582 --> 01:14:03,223
Step back

824
01:14:04,662 --> 01:14:06,484
Welcome to America.

825
01:14:06,580 --> 01:14:09,936
Now don't unpack.
You won't be staying long.

826
01:14:10,056 --> 01:14:11,230
Agent Crawford...

827
01:14:11,350 --> 01:14:12,909
I'm a busy man.

828
01:14:14,895 --> 01:14:16,626
Oh, we got a lot of business,
you and me.

829
01:14:16,746 --> 01:14:19,335
I think you know that.

830
01:14:19,431 --> 01:14:22,500
Three years ago
Rogue killed my partner and his family.

831
01:14:22,596 --> 01:14:23,459
And you know what?

832
01:14:23,579 --> 01:14:25,377
Rogue was working for you.

833
01:14:26,911 --> 01:14:29,476
Rogue is a myth. Just a rumor.

834
01:14:29,596 --> 01:14:31,288
You think so, huh.

835
01:14:38,132 --> 01:14:40,985
You can't always trust rumors, can you?

836
01:14:41,105 --> 01:14:45,133
Rogue turns around and fucking slices
up the heavy hitters you sent with him.

837
01:14:45,325 --> 01:14:48,585
Now you gotta ask yourself, now
why would he do something like that?

838
01:14:48,681 --> 01:14:50,887
I've never seen this man
before in my life.

839
01:14:55,682 --> 01:14:56,737
Look...

840
01:14:56,857 --> 01:14:59,974
I don't care if you fuckers slaughter
each other till you're all dead and buried.

841
01:15:00,094 --> 01:15:02,203
Truth is it makes my job a lot easier.

842
01:15:02,299 --> 01:15:05,464
But if I find proof that
ties any of this shit back to you...

843
01:15:05,676 --> 01:15:08,155
you ain't never gonna see Japan again.

844
01:15:08,275 --> 01:15:11,122
And neither will that
pretty little daughter of yours.

845
01:15:14,304 --> 01:15:15,656
Thanks for the tip

846
01:15:15,776 --> 01:15:17,068
Agent Crawford.

847
01:16:09,076 --> 01:16:12,476
Finally! My most loyal stranger.

848
01:16:12,596 --> 01:16:14,322
We meet face to face.

849
01:16:22,858 --> 01:16:26,694
Yanagawa-san, I've waited
a long time for this moment.

850
01:16:28,995 --> 01:16:33,503
It's all because of you
that we now have this opportunity.

851
01:16:33,623 --> 01:16:37,339
Kira enjoyed working with you here.

852
01:16:37,459 --> 01:16:42,038
One day she'll make a fine leader
of Yanagawa clan.

853
01:16:42,326 --> 01:16:47,888
Yeah, one day.
I'm reminded of the Sengoku...

854
01:16:50,041 --> 01:16:54,218
when the Daimyo warriors fought
each other to unite Japan.

855
01:16:54,410 --> 01:16:59,492
The one who finally succeeded was
a man by the name of Oda Nobunaga.

856
01:17:00,539 --> 01:17:03,113
And do you know how he did it?

857
01:17:03,233 --> 01:17:06,277
He killed everyone who opposed him.

858
01:17:06,397 --> 01:17:10,617
Thanks to you all those
who oppose me here are dead.

859
01:17:10,737 --> 01:17:12,823
I exist but to serve you.

860
01:17:26,389 --> 01:17:29,510
In Asia these could never be sold.

861
01:17:30,922 --> 01:17:33,538
But the fortune
they will bring here in the West...

862
01:17:33,658 --> 01:17:37,414
will be more than enough
to continue our American expansion.

863
01:17:37,534 --> 01:17:40,635
And now it is time for your reward.

864
01:17:40,730 --> 01:17:41,785
Open it.

865
01:18:01,451 --> 01:18:04,490
One must remove all future threats.

866
01:18:04,610 --> 01:18:09,405
You allowed that threat to remain
by not killing the woman and child.

867
01:18:12,987 --> 01:18:17,749
You have disobeyed me
and broken my most sacred code.

868
01:18:18,228 --> 01:18:20,242
Your code, not mine.

869
01:18:22,165 --> 01:18:24,653
Betrayal cannot be forgiven.

870
01:18:26,052 --> 01:18:28,370
Take him downstairs.

871
01:18:28,684 --> 01:18:31,847
Persuade him to tell us
where the wife and child are.

872
01:18:42,251 --> 01:18:44,602
They are truly magnificent.

873
01:18:46,232 --> 01:18:49,684
So many dead for such small trinkets.

874
01:18:53,584 --> 01:18:54,767
Fakes!

875
01:20:00,844 --> 01:20:02,163
Find the woman and child...

876
01:20:02,283 --> 01:20:03,913
They'll lead us to the real Horses.

877
01:20:18,688 --> 01:20:19,833
Yanagawa-san!

878
01:20:56,084 --> 01:20:58,865
After all these years...

879
01:20:59,057 --> 01:21:01,527
why do you do this?

880
01:21:01,647 --> 01:21:03,373
You ordered the hit.

881
01:21:05,291 --> 01:21:08,264
I ordered many hits.

882
01:21:10,661 --> 01:21:12,963
This one was different.

883
01:21:54,602 --> 01:21:58,613
You should have left
the wife and daughter alone.

884
01:22:26,365 --> 01:22:28,726
I left none to seek revenge.

885
01:22:35,664 --> 01:22:37,549
You left one!

886
01:23:03,937 --> 01:23:07,854
Your assassin, Rogue,
never made it out alive.

887
01:23:16,965 --> 01:23:20,418
So, you are Tom Lone?

888
01:23:21,952 --> 01:23:25,309
Changing your face, your voice.

889
01:23:27,626 --> 01:23:29,912
All so you could get to me.

890
01:23:33,099 --> 01:23:36,721
Pain can be a weapon,
if you so choose.

891
01:23:41,650 --> 01:23:46,216
How do you think we found out
you were FBI in the first place?

892
01:23:46,336 --> 01:23:47,654
It was Crawford.

893
01:23:57,628 --> 01:23:59,658
You killed my family.

894
01:23:59,778 --> 01:24:03,574
It was Crawford.
He's the one who gave you up.

895
01:24:07,506 --> 01:24:09,616
Crawford works for me.

896
01:24:14,239 --> 01:24:17,863
Because of him your family's dead!

897
01:24:19,935 --> 01:24:21,071
Somebody talked.

898
01:24:21,191 --> 01:24:23,522
From inside. Close to us.

899
01:24:23,905 --> 01:24:25,727
You never know who's working for who.

900
01:24:25,919 --> 01:24:27,070
Somebody talked.

901
01:25:19,243 --> 01:25:20,296
Crawford?

902
01:25:22,467 --> 01:25:23,653
Shiro's dead.

903
01:25:29,336 --> 01:25:31,708
Get out of this business
while you can, Goi.

904
01:26:37,881 --> 01:26:41,334
From America? Leave me.

905
01:27:13,404 --> 01:27:14,228
Crawford.

906
01:27:15,628 --> 01:27:18,040
Remember the night we met?

907
01:27:18,160 --> 01:27:20,534
I remember my partner
blowing your face off.

908
01:27:20,654 --> 01:27:24,202
You live today
only because of what he did.

909
01:27:26,321 --> 01:27:29,765
I live today only to kill you,
you miserable prick.

910
01:27:30,458 --> 01:27:32,354
Meet me there.

911
01:27:42,903 --> 01:27:43,766
Goi

912
01:27:54,508 --> 01:27:55,754
Where are you?

913
01:27:56,336 --> 01:27:57,768
Show yourself!

914
01:27:59,847 --> 01:28:03,139
I got your surgeon.
He made a positive ID.

915
01:28:06,581 --> 01:28:09,370
Come on, Crawford. Flush him out.

916
01:28:09,901 --> 01:28:11,578
It's over, Rogue.

917
01:28:12,857 --> 01:28:14,551
Can you hear me?

918
01:30:08,819 --> 01:30:10,593
Why did you do it?

919
01:30:11,361 --> 01:30:14,491
What did Shiro promise you
that was worth my life

920
01:30:14,611 --> 01:30:17,115
and the life of Diane and Amy?

921
01:30:26,513 --> 01:30:30,445
No, you're not him. It can't be.

922
01:30:55,380 --> 01:30:57,466
You don't even sound like him.

923
01:30:57,586 --> 01:30:59,681
Look at my eyes, John.

924
01:30:59,801 --> 01:31:02,573
The one thing the surgeons
can never change.

925
01:31:35,235 --> 01:31:36,943
Oh, Jesus, Tom.

926
01:31:37,751 --> 01:31:40,046
Is it really you?

927
01:31:40,166 --> 01:31:41,221
Yeah.

928
01:31:42,555 --> 01:31:44,194
Why didn't you tell me?

929
01:31:46,535 --> 01:31:50,044
It was the only way
I could get the man responsible.

930
01:31:50,737 --> 01:31:52,230
But all along...

931
01:31:52,614 --> 01:31:55,990
I never thought it would
bring me back to my best friend.

932
01:31:59,201 --> 01:32:01,333
I didn't know they'd send Rogue.

933
01:32:01,453 --> 01:32:03,673
For Christ sakes,
I thought he was dead!

934
01:32:03,793 --> 01:32:06,156
They said they wanted
to teach you a lesson.

935
01:32:06,276 --> 01:32:10,568
For shooting Rogue.
Just rough you up a bit, that's all.

936
01:32:10,821 --> 01:32:13,572
Is that what they told you?

937
01:32:13,692 --> 01:32:16,034
Shiro ordered everything.

938
01:32:17,193 --> 01:32:22,268
I tried to stop working for him,
to get out, so many times.

939
01:32:24,676 --> 01:32:26,281
I thought if I could make
that son of a bitch

940
01:32:26,401 --> 01:32:30,000
pay for what he did to you, somehow
it would make things right again.

941
01:32:35,406 --> 01:32:37,492
You think you could forgive me, Tom?

942
01:32:37,612 --> 01:32:39,147
Tom Lone is dead.

943
01:32:39,827 --> 01:32:41,448
My name is Rogue.

944
01:32:42,925 --> 01:32:44,033
No...

945
01:32:49,524 --> 01:32:50,463
Shit!

